      "content": "it's hard to even think about therapy or talking to people when there's just... nothing there to talk to. it feels like a joke. how can you fix a person who isn't even there anymore? the music, the vision, the drive... that was the \"me\" part. without it, i'm just a biological machine going through the motions. it feels more like a burden than a life at this point.",
